The,SMSPoint,API,allows,users,to,send,thousands,of,SMS,messages,to,contacts,clients,or,employees,from,a,website,SMSpoint,offers,bulk,text,messaging,delivery,to,any,country,in,the,world,via,a,simple,HTTP,API,Features,include,the,ability,to,produce,delivery,reports,and,receive,messages,sent,to,a,specified,inbox,The,API,uses,RESTful,protocol,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML,Coverage,in,countries